description: This cool kind crew is cranking out quite a few cookies, and with this truck, they’re taking their crunchy, chewy, and crazy-tasty baked treats straight to the Atlanta streets! Their delectable selection includes all the classics (Chocolate Chip, Oatmeal, Peanut Butter, Sugar, etc…), and some Signature kinds that everyone digs (Cranberry Oatmeal, Peanut Butter Chocolate Chip w/Pretzel, Red Velvet White Chocolate Chip w/Macadamia Nut, etc..), as well as a few Cookies Cakes and yummy Bars too! They may not be as famous as other brands...but with the quality of ingredients they’re using to craft these gourmet cookie creations (including real butter), you’ll most likely find these treats to be even better.
name: Not As Famous Cookie Company
